Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.91,lottery_2,A,0000,0000,0000,,Lottery
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.59,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.91,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs! Hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:20.41,Win,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(233,1)}Win a stay at Kiriyako Hot Springs Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We get a hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.11,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd rather have third prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:29.67,Prize R,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Every home needs one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:29.67,Prize L,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cook anything\N with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:29.67,Third,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Third Prize
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:32.59,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs! Hot springs! Hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:35.50,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You like hot springs that much, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:38.93,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What's a hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.37,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:46.10,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big bath that you go \Nin with other people, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:51.57,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is it bigger than the bath in your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:52.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:54.84,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is it bigger than a lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:56.80,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:00:59.87,Lottery,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Lottery Ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:02.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If we win, you can see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.16,0:01:11.34,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs! Hot springs! Hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:21.10,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:23.10,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:02.87,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(795,480)}True Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.37,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.75,Second,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Second \NPrize
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.15,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.75,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.37,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We have a first prize winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.39,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.88,Bead,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Certificate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.43,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.38,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.26,Free,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Free Accommodation Coupon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.68,Nonoka,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.19,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.78,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:42.70,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is a rare sight, \Nseeing you help at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:47.12,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Not as rare as someone who'd go help \Nat someone else's shop, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.95,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted me to. \NWhat was I supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:53.08,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu wanted you to. \NWhat were you supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.14,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:55.72,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get ready to move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:56.94,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Today's my last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:57.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.47,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get those?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.34,free_lodging,,0000,0000,0000,,Free Lodging Coupon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:07.51,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The lady from the hotel \Ncame and invited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.85,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the hot springs would be \Nnice once in a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.73,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.60,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't even ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.70,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Who would go with their own sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.74,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:25.46,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well now that we agree \Non something, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.62,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting in the way of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:33.84,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, can I ask you for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.54,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,No changes today, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.58,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.47,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:53.24,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shione, look! Shione—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:05.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:06.93,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.93,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,An acquaintance gave me these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:14.50,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She told me I should invite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:15.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.67,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.53,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:20.50,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.01,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.27,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take that from someone \NI don't really even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.52,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.44,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,In fact she's really straightforward \Nand easy to get to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.22,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.53,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Next weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.71,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:43.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The hot springs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.20,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with the \Nrest of these coupons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.68,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.69,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yuzuki, want to come \Nto the hot springs with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.46,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:59.15,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.46,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.97,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any coupons left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.07,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:27.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:28.27,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The hot springs—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:30.26,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.32,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.58,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I can go to the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.19,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.49,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the hot springs \Ntogether on her next break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.60,Nonoka,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Call from \NNonoka
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.26,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the shop for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:00.53,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:02.60,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so Noel couldn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.43,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But you can come, right, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:12.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.24,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Koharu what to do \Nabout the rest of the coupons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's someone she wants to invite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind just \Nthe three of us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:24.51,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see, she has some left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.40,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.77,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Koharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.76,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Next weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.61,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's leftover curry in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Heat it up if you're going to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on low heat so it doesn't splatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.17,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to make it, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you have to eat your salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You're too fussy about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.39,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:13.13,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And don't leave the dishes \Nout once you're done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It gets really hard to wash them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.17,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:24.17,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.53,Hotel,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyako Hot Springs Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.28,sora-internal,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.36,sora-internal,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.60,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:44.15,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:48.29,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about \Nleaving Dad by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:49.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Koharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.94,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She should be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we aren't really late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:57.80,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:05.19,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's something I want\N to tell you before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.82,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.70,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.18,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:29.92,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, I'll come later next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,H-How's the shop? It's a weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.80,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.72,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.78,Buns,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer Steamed Buns
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,They're selling them here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,They have good reach, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.70,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,They don't taste bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.49,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,but they were better when \NI ate them as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:08.18,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:10.93,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,They're still the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.61,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shiihara Saucer Steamed Buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.41,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.19,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.53,Outdoor,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1030,1)}Outdoor Baths\N{\fs20}(Down the hall and to the right.)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.62,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they have outdoor baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.02,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.67,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.48,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:51.54,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs, hot springs,\N hot springs with Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.59,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty nice view.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.35,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.28,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:10:59.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.89,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I approve of the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.37,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're just in a cease fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.39,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:12.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting all comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:15.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You know there's something \Nwe have to do first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.70,sora-main,Koharu; Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:20.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go to the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.20,sora-main,Koharu; Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.31,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.48,sora-main,Koharu; Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.91,Cleaning,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning\N{\fs20}No Access
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.66,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We're a bit too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.30,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:48.86,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:52.13,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there something \Nyou needed to do, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:55.56,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have to say \Nsomething to Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.40,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.72,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.07,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.24,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.52,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.42,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:10.91,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:12.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.79,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.08,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.09,Champ,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Champion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.21,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You are the champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.10,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want \Nto talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.55,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.01,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.61,Arcade,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Arcade
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.07,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The notice fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.62,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm playing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.12,Order,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Out of Order
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.87,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.75,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.65,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.71,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:27.16,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I actually asked Koharu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.39,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,to invite you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.10,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It was suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.47,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe if we're \Nin a different environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.93,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be easier for me to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:53.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.49,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it out of my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.20,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,that I did something so awful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:22.38,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,So if you're going to forgive me, \Nhit me really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:28.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.39,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,As hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.79,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.73,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I said as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:55.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be fair if I got serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.95,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So we're even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.12,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.83,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.76,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be here \Nin this town next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:24.28,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She could have invited me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.78,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should clean you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So it must have been that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.98,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.58,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.73,Bunny,Text,0000,0000,0000,,White Bunny of the Snow Country
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.73,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.07,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like the saucer, Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.47,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you ask such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.84,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You're always taking pictures of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.87,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.37,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,to learn about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.46,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We're eating, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:23.79,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.19,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:50.26,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Good, it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.43,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see without my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.70,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What if it wasn't me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.89,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.60,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:05.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you invited me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.03,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.01,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.91,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Noel can come next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.28,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And Togawa-san, if it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.73,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:23.91,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.84,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That was refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:28.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:30.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's buy something cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:31.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.82,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Woo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.61,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Take your clothes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.06,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,This is all a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.67,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.12,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.73,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.75,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.88,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun bathing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:58.16,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,A bath is a bath, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.38,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you're with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.58,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I feel warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.15,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you texting Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.11,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.65,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I had him help at the store. \NI have to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:18.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:19.66,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to say \Nyou wanted him to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:23.27,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.49,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you have someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.20,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,So boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.56,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:50.11,sora-internal,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,When's the last time I wasn't alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:05.83,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.49,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.52,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.27,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You could have shopped at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.87,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.05,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. For Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And for Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.99,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.45,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Can we come over \Nto your place someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.04,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.54,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,The hot springs were so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.99,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.05,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:00.20,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.28,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.41,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:08.06,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, right, Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.27,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:15.81,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to make \Nany more friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.01,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. You like the saucer, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:19.99,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:25.32,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't walk around with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.70,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,A real nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Soup curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.81,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I tried making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:55.87,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But we should finish the leftovers first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.03,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:10.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to let it burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.93,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:16.87,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:21.63,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I figured she might like it \Nout here more than in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.76,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:39.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you for a favor.
